Ask HN: How to hide plugin/ theme details to public in WordPress
text:
Hey I am using wordpress for one of the client, and he is having a product which is USP for him and the whole website is built on wordpress, so his concerns are that some website like this website https://wpdetector.com/ it detects all the plugins and themes being used in the mentioned website.
My question is how we as a company can hide these details from websites like these, If we are able to hide all the details then it would be very great else we would like to hide as much as we want.
Kindly answer this query of mine.

Ask HN: Why isn't there a bank that stores your money and charges fees for it?
text:
I would definitely put some money there. Wonder why there is no such service.

Edit: I mean a bank that doesn't do anything with your money e.g. putting out loan or buying bond with it. Therefore, your money would be theoretically safe.

text: I see it’s common for people on HN to have a personal website/blog. I’m interested in knowing if the creation and maintenance of a personal website have lead to paid full/part time jobs, increased learning, brought new connections to others or are purely vanity.
